Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂… 笹原前辈!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:13.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}没事儿没事儿～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我本来就是因为对星星感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并不是被加贺带过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞 这样么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你们看起来关系很好的样子还以为肯定在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我和七濑只是单纯的家很近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一说是青梅竹马就总这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我对七濑可是什么想法都没有!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也什么想法都没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且加贺他 似乎有其他喜欢的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔诶! 是这样么加贺君?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才没呢 这种事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嘛～ 虽说看你这样就大概知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要我帮你猜猜么～? 嗯～～～?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原 坂本老师说找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶～ 正是关键时刻的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我过下再来听后续呐～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然是笹原前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:04.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想想加贺你也不会对星星有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看上前辈了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以说不是了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且这和七濑你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为啥总是关心这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想你快点被拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为啥啊! 我得罪你啦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:20.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你从上中学后开始 就一直无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就因为怕被周围同学嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,还不是七濑你说不要的吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说要是被误解为那种关系的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是不想被认为和你关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈!? 这我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊～这样啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超不想和我有什么绯闻的是吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么鬼啊!? 我这边不是在为七濑你担心么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说什么为我担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明就是你突然不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,七濑你不也是 突然就开始讨厌我了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是加贺你先讨厌我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哪边先都无所谓吧 反正是相互讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是讨厌你的话哪会和你上一个学校啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈…哈!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,完全不懂你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笨蛋加贺! 还不懂我么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明和其他女孩子可以很正常的说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就单单无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不… 我没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算如此你对别人看起来也没太关心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我还一直以为你对别的女生应该没什么兴趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等等… 你冷静一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为啥 是笹原前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,知道了啦对不起是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有考虑到七濑的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一直 在为我的事情担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那个 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是你青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是我青梅竹马怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你啥都没搞明白不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真以为我为加贺你做这么多…  就只是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是说不讨厌我么…刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最讨厌你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到 到底是讨厌我啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你跑到天文部来到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,来气我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,久等啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,撒～加贺君你喜欢的女孩子到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}结\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟喜欢的人表白 然后在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但那之后总感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,变得有些拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚 刚田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天一起回…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉上根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我还有社团活动 下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是做朋友比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不不 这才刚开始交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我应该更加主动一点才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:37.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了上根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,还没回家么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也有一些事情没做完留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 让你等我才是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我社团活动的时候也会待到比较晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以以后一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 太晚了很危险的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是有刚田君在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我只能送你到公交车站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然他其实不愿我交往么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,给他徒添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不会的 刚田君只是太温柔了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一直以来都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚刚… 是躲开我了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,躲开我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:24.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,社团活动出了汗所以在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实并不是在躲着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 可以不要这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我应该早点跟你说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟人交往我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也在学习该如何做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我也考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以希望上根能放轻松一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本不该这样子说的但…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 谢谢你跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,谢谢你跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉 我没打算把你弄哭来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:13.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没事 我们还能回到以前那样么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢 但和以前完全一样也不现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是啊 都是我的错 变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下次要不要试着牵牵手?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,毕竟是恋人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我太急了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 刚刚像要分手一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:36.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,分手!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我可没说这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是想互相之间注意些 别那么拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能再稍微轻松一点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,难道说 只有我很在意这问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:52.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 那啥 刚在一起就摆出一副男朋友的架子也很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:57.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以那个 本想尽可能像平时那样相处…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是这样又不会太冷淡了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想先关心下你回家的安全什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是我多管闲事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:10.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…刚刚我靠近你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为什么避开了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这个…因为社团活动出了汗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 其实是因为有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 刚刚是七濑她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,优树 去给七濑家送点苹果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不要 妈妈你自己去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,干嘛这么不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟薰酱吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不是这样 总觉得自己被讨厌着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈? 薰酱喜欢你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 这还是秘密的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不算不算 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 我们不需要妹纸
